"2 1/2 pounds sweet potatoes, peeled and cut into 1 1/2-inch chunks","1 1/2 tablespoons molasses","1 1/4 teaspoons cinnamon","1 teaspoon kosher salt","1/4 teaspoon allspice","1/4 teaspoon nutmeg","2  large eggs, lightly beaten","2 tablespoons unsalted butter","1  red apple, such as Rome, and 1 green apple, both halved, cored and cut into 1-inch cubes","1/3 cup sliced almonds"